## Possible Improvements
This project can be expanded by:
- generating multiple failed logins intentionally and comparing timestamps
- documenting different logon types
- correlating Event ID 4625 with successful login events such as 4624
- exporting logs for further analysis
- creating a detection rule for repeated failed logins

